description:
“Wow you are really tall!” I said as I met Wes for the first time.
“Yeah,” he said, looking at the ground. “I was one of the tallest kids in my class.”
He is tall! He’s a little over 6’3” with a lanky, smooth swimmer’s build.
I could tell right away that Wes was a shy one. He’s very soft spoken.
He had mentioned that he’s on the swim team at school. I tried to get him to talk about it but he was a little hesitant.
Oddly, he wasn’t shy at all about getting naked!
title: Wes
